        Parameters:
        id - Unique ID for the module.
        name - Module name that will be displayed in the menu.
        description - Module description. Also will be displayed in the menu.
        type - Module type.
        optionsGui - Options GUI. If not null, an options button will display in the menu.
        widget - Module widget. If not null, the widget will be rendered in-game.
